text: Axa is a French insurance company. It may also refer to: * Axa (comics), a comic strip by Donne Avenell and Romero, about Axa, a barbarian woman of the future * Alpha Chi Alpha, a fraternity at Dartmouth College * Anguilla, a British Overseas Territory in the Caribbean * AXA, IATA code for the Clayton J. Lloyd International Airport in Anguilla ==See also== * Al-Aqsa (disambiguation)
title: AXA (disambiguation)
